  "title": "Monsoon Mediterranean Almond Crumble",
  "description": "A herbal and chewy mediterranean-friendly dish featuring almond paste, caramelized flavors, with a Ukrainian twist.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean, Ukrainian",
  "diet": [
    "vegan",
